    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/e31b808a5587544de7b10aa51420cfcb.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1560 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/7a0392ed670d9be5fd5506c8b304451e.poster.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/7a0392ed670d9be5fd5506c8b304451e.webm?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/7a0392ed670d9be5fd5506c8b304451e.mp4?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Astra Sentinel</i>《<i>星界哨兵</i>》<i>是一款波次生存RTS，无尽的外星虫群不断攻击你的行星。建设防御、管理资源，在持续压力下扩展领土。每一个决定都至关重要，一次突破可能意味着彻底毁灭。面对不断升级的威胁，调整策略，尽可能长时间生存下去。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/0afd0c0dacdf7c26e44237412f7ff7c5.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1560 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/0d90bb6ea891dcb1a483fd29a5fe6a8e.poster.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/0d90bb6ea891dcb1a483fd29a5fe6a8e.webm?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/0d90bb6ea891dcb1a483fd29a5fe6a8e.mp4?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>在多样化的行星上扩展你的帝国，同时在其表面建造建筑和防御工事，并参与激烈的太空战斗。可无缝切换行星视角和轨道视角，无需加载屏幕，实时管理两线作战。利用每颗行星的资源提高生产力，加强舰队，保护帝国免受无情威胁。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/9e8de21d7dc7796fc46656334b9256a9.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1560 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/20f180246c1593463247fe0bb7680987.poster.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/20f180246c1593463247fe0bb7680987.webm?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/20f180246c1593463247fe0bb7680987.mp4?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>挑战具有26个可扩展难度等级的生存模式，威胁永无止境。提升玩家等级，解锁强力新单位，增强现有部队，以应对越来越严苛的战局。通过无数种方式扩展、战斗和生存，每一次游玩都是独一无二的，为战略实验和重复游戏提供无限可能。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/0c91a19b579bbdb041164aa3c6ad26a4.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1560 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/686e23e31b57539f83b1ca791efbb970.poster.avif?t=1772184369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/686e23e31b57539f83b1ca791efbb970.webm?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/686e23e31b57539f83b1ca791efbb970.mp4?t=1772184369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>体验精心制作的故事战役，每个任务都具有独特目标和挑战。在威胁灭绝的外星入侵下，领导人类进行银河再征服。遇见难忘的角色，做出艰难选择，在考验战术能力的激烈战斗中生存。每个任务都讲述一个故事，将战略深度与叙事进度结合，带来真正沉浸的体验。</i></p>",
